{
  "stem": "7160.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Where was this?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we took them there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the beginning we don't know, so finally, you know, we cross them, across the border, with no problems the first time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On foot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, on foot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Once you cross the American border, you go to the American side, there's no problems.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Over there on the Russian side was bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So once we cross the border we took them to the American side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my part was as far as sometimes to leave them in Germany where the American watch, or sometimes take them to Austria.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we cross over there no problems.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A few times we run into trouble.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Couple of times, matter of fact, we run into Jew Russian soldiers, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We spoke Yiddish I say, guy, guy, guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, go fast, because if they catch him, you know, they can get in trouble.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If they catches us we can get in big trouble too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a couple times we got problems.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes we used to give them a case of vodka, you know, to share it out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of the soldiers look around then and let it go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we did it maybe about 20 times maybe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So sometimes when I'm in trouble we had to do what we have to do to get it over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To take them over the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I have a picture from then when I transferred, if you want to see it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have when we arrive in the American side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stopped in a forest everybody was freezing to death, and light a big fire there to warm it up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was watching around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had my gun in the hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
